tion is provided to the sub-floor - by un-blocking air-bricks or introducing new ones. If joists are thinner than insulation, may be necessary to under-draw floor with more rigid but still breathable insulating board. \",\"maintenance\":\"MINIMAL\",\"lib\":\"FLIT_01\",\"type\":\"Floor\",\"l\":0,\"h\":0,\"perimeter\":9.6,\"area\":11,\"id\":8,\"location\":\"Conservatory Floor\",\"g\":\"\",\"gL\":\"\",\"ff\":\"\",\"netarea\":11,\"windowarea\":0,\"wk\":2.2,\"quantity\":11,\"cost_total\":880}},\"9\":{\"original_element\":{\"type\":\"Loft\",\"name\":\"150mm fibre loft insulation\",\"lib\":\"LRI_01.5\",\"l\":\"\",\"h\":0,\"area\":103,\"uvalue\":0.3,\"id\":9,\"location\":\"Main house\",\"description\":\"Insulated loft space below pitched tiled or slated roof. \",\"kvalue\":9,\"g\":\"\",\"gL\":\"\",\"ff\":\"\",\"performance\":\"\",\"benefits\":\"\",\"cost\":\"\",\"who_by\":\"\",\"disruption\":\"\",\"associated_work\":\"\",\"notes\":\"\",\"maintenance\":\"\",\"netarea\":103,\"windowarea\":0,\"wk\":30.9},\"measure\":{\"name\":\"400mm fibre loft insulation\",\"description\":\"Loft insulation increased to 400mm depth and topped with highly vapour permeable breather membrane to reduce thermal bypass. Vapour-check and air-tightness membrane can also be fitted below insulation and on top of ceiling, if existing insulation can be moved and ceiling can be accessed. This will improve air-tightness and further reduce condensation risks. \",\"source\":\"URBED\\/ SAP table 1e, p.195\",\"uvalue\":0.11,\"kvalue\":9,\"tags\":[\"Loft\"],\"performance\":\"0.11 W\\/K.m2\",\"benefits\":\"Fuel Bills   Carbon Emissions   Comfort \",\"cost\":\"15\",\"cost_units\":\"sqm\",\"who_by\":\"DIY or General Contractor\",\"disruption\":\"MINIMAL\",\"associated_work\":\"Loft Hatch, Loft Storage, Roof Insulation, Internal\\/Cavity\\/External Wall Insulation, air-tightness works\",\"key_risks\":\"Condensation in loft space or trapped within insulation build up. \",\"notes\":\"Any cold loft space needs to be ve